sequenceDiagram
    participant PlatformOp as ODH Platform Operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ModuleOp as MCP Lifecycle<br/>Module Operator
    participant KustProv as KustomizeProvider<br/>(embedded manifests)
    participant GC as Garbage Collector<br/>(odh-platform-utilities)

    rect rgb(220, 240, 220)
        Note over PlatformOp,GC: Flow 1: Operand Deployment (managementState=Managed)

        PlatformOp->>K8sAPI: Create MCPLifecycleOperator CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>ModuleOp: Watch event: MCPLifecycleOperator created

        ModuleOp->>KustProv: Load embedded operand manifests
        KustProv-->>ModuleOp: Rendered manifests<br/>(namespace/image/labels applied)

        ModuleOp->>K8sAPI: SSA Apply operand resources<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Note right of K8sAPI: Creates: Deployment, ServiceAccount,<br/>ClusterRoles, ClusterRoleBindings,<br/>MCPServer CRD, Metrics Service

        ModuleOp->>GC: Build desiredSet from rendered manifests
        GC->>K8sAPI: List resources with label<br/>platform.opendatahub.io/part-of=mcplifecycleoperator<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>GC: Labeled resources
        GC->>K8sAPI: Delete stale resources NOT in desiredSet<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token

        ModuleOp->>K8sAPI: Check operand Deployment readiness<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>ModuleOp: Deployment status

        ModuleOp->>K8sAPI: Patch MCPLifecycleOperator status<br/>Conditions: Ready, ProvisioningSucceeded,<br/>MCPLifecycleOperatorAvailable<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over PlatformOp,GC: Flow 2: Operand Teardown (managementState=Removed)

        PlatformOp->>K8sAPI: Update MCPLifecycleOperator CR<br/>spec.managementState=Removed<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        K8sAPI-->>ModuleOp: Watch event: MCPLifecycleOperator updated

        ModuleOp->>K8sAPI: Delete all resources with label<br/>platform.opendatahub.io/part-of=mcplifecycleoperator<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Note right of K8sAPI: Removes: Deployment, ServiceAccount,<br/>ClusterRoles, ClusterRoleBindings,<br/>MCPServer CRD, Metrics Service

        ModuleOp->>K8sAPI: Patch MCPLifecycleOperator status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end
